description.en:
What is the project about?
$CUT is an offensive meme project that goes against the grain of conventional cryptocurrency projects. $CUT is pro-free speech and carries the message inside of it's offensive nature.

What makes your project unique?
$CUT is the only meme project where the participants actively have a shared goal besides increasing the token price. $CUT community members are engaged in protecting freedom of speech and use $CUT as a conduit.

History of your project.
20-04-2023 Launch
14-5-2023 600k market cap broken

What’s next for your project?
We are partnering up with The Dev from the famous memecoin $DBI

What can your token be used for?
$CUT token holders get access to a gated community but also the power to financially support what they believe in. Together they're one community
